{
  "stem": "3771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was-- to be truthfully speaking, even those who didn't believe it, there was nowhere to hide.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even if you run away after the ghetto, most of the Polacks-- the Germans gave them, that you will become, like-- what do you call it-- two pounds of sugar if you will find a Jew there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nowhere to hide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nowhere to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you have to realize that the starvation, and [INAUDIBLE] with the ghetto, you were-- you're [? worse than ?] half-human.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The degradation, the horror of it-- but it was the most horrifying of things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we had to start transporting to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the transport was horrifying [INAUDIBLE] things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember we was, maybe, 3,000 or 4,000 in our transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were forced, by foot, to go to the station, surrounded by Germans with vicious dogs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the horrifying thing they said, that each one was-- shall take the most valuable things with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people took the most valuable things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, make sure your name is there and your address is there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everyone-- so older people were carrying rucksacks with all their belongings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] that maybe needed-- jewelry or from the home, silverware, everything that you could carry, because you would need it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some have to carry some [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] even utensils.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] think you will need it for this, or for the children this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the journey to Auschwitz was the most horrifying thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took maybe about two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister had a little boy, Yehuda.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was bitterly crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no water, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
